 
<p>
US citizens: call on Congress
<a href="https://environmental-action.webaction.org/p/dia/action4/common/public/?action_KEY=54281&supporter_KEY=229474">to defeat Boebert's bill</a>
to eliminate
endangered species protection for wolves.
<p>
To sign without
<a href="https://gnu.org/philosophy/javascript-trap.html">running nonfree JavaScript</a>
code from the web site, use the <a href="/salsalabs-method.html">Salsalabs workaround</a>.
<p>
To see the confirmation statement in your browser, erase the CSS from
it.  IceCat has a command to do that in the right-click menu.

